description:
#219: On this episode we sit down with Farrah Brittany. Farrah is the daughter of Real Housewives Of Beverly Hills Co-Star Kyle Richards, a top real estate agent in Los Angeles with The Agency. On this episode we discuss how Farrah balances a massive real estate career & a life showcased on reality tv. We also dive into productivity hacks, morning routines, and what it takes to have a high performance career.
